Horse for Flightgear

Follow the horses by Helicopter :)
Steer the horsee with aileron control. "," is Brake and "." is Accelerator. 

If you have rudder pedals with Toebrakes, the left pedal is Brake and 
the right is Accelerator.

M (Shift-m) engages Reverse, m disengages reverse.


by Marc Kraus
Lake of Constance Hangar
http://www.marc-kraus.de/fg/

This model is now released under the terms of the GPLv2 with permission by the author


